{"tid":1438994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再開po乜乜乜點點點就黎輸好快輸嘅都 係鬼 係推東方記者個肥矮差婆 比狗屌","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:47:27.000Z","uid":265197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3fba9efc8935fbe6d798844df197881cb7ba189c","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"膠po要推上熱門有幾難<br />\n好似今日有知咩女朋友比人拉左嘅po成2千正皮<br />\n但一起底就會見到唔對路<br />\n見到膠po咪撚理咪得囉<br />\n起底 block 上一頁 有幾撚難<br />\n膠po分化mon po狗不嬲都有嫁喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問題係你班撚樣走入去配合佢呀<br />\n走入去同個擺明帶人遊花園嘅假膠嘈做乜撚野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成個6月7月有無日日係度咩咩咩我地就黎輸嘅po?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n成日都吹奏呢d乜乜柒柒就黎輸嘅風<br />\nd勝利球迷一見少少野就驚死落錯注咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家香港係得番2條路簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一係就個政府冚家產<br />\n一係就攬炒<br />\n信用評分國民教育人面辯識23條網路實名都會黎<br />\n傾乜撚如果有1 2條要求都接受姐<br />\n無得番以前咁嫁喇<br />\n就算無晒示威無晒反對聲音<br />\n班黑警一樣咁濫權亂鳩咁拉人嫁</span></span>"},{"pid":"9e3c65e1ddd800a4ec4d23a9337d3a47caeb00cc","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ada8dddec01a2db11da1e6a940eed151629dfad","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c260806dc9f3292cd17d61840d404439990fee","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d55872011c7c797f3b3a72b31c3df7a0a5075f","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e43537c92ae20079c79555be8e13cc91151411","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25508a29ffe879aee4fcea76fd869fae6a28cf67","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02476968de3ef4e12a250ea39456ce6162a098d8","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0ec0058e85b6dc7ea5b0f7478adb4d56c9c792","tid":1438994,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}